{"tid":969371,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"世紀大決鬥 軟雪糕vs雪條！","createTime":"2019-01-05T04:19:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-05T20:49:23.000Z","uid":47123,"like":196,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"90f65d21ffcfb93eda0eb046a162efbb5e8ab4f5","tid":969371,"uid":47123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T04:19:07.000Z","msg":"其實之前都有決鬥過<br />\n當時題目係雪糕vs雪條 雪糕大勝<br />\n依家題目再specific啲<br />\n兩者唔可以有脆皮有nuts<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要用口感味道取勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n軟雪糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n首先出場嘅係絕版彩虹新地筒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jHonMKm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjHonMKm.png&h=b54e4155&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後係愈嚟愈貴嘅雪糕車<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YCoGhQ2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYCoGhQ2.png&h=647dcfda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有新年特別版 士多啤梨味<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HE5pZ4C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHE5pZ4C.png&h=f230260f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由日本派出奶味超級重嘅代表<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BMrgRbi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBMrgRbi.png&h=c31ba658&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後係近排熱潮好似散退咗嘅綠茶<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kr0QVC0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkr0QVC0.png&h=4aaf6f9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雪條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n懷舊time 因為都絕得七七八八<br />\n相信大家都識 唔介紹咁多了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vC7vVFq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvC7vVFq.png&h=3597e3e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RfD3weB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRfD3weB.png&h=ab64887d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/62xjO1g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F62xjO1g.png&h=00faf308&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UHGTTsX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUHGTTsX.png&h=1f8b9a78&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YkxS81i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYkxS81i.png&h=06940c04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上列只作參考 我一時淨係記得咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n記得要係淨係軟雪糕雪條<br />\n唔可以有其他配料<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n投票喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d51bf8ca705fee7fa6780f5d8a0e65a35cbf323","tid":969371,"uid":47123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T04:22:05.000Z","msg":"雖然雪條款款都係回憶<br />\n但我唔念舊情<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個係美食家嘅專業！"},{"pid":"4fc0691b7a46b20c31dca88cab9843337ae65d09","tid":969371,"uid":15950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d51bf8ca705fee7fa6780f5d8a0e65a35cbf323","tid":969371,"uid":47123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T04:22:05.000Z","msg":"雖然雪條款款都係回憶<br />\n但我唔念舊情<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個係美食家嘅專業！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T04:26:15.000Z","msg":"你係雪糕派嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4030f0b89ef701e45edc571f85c93a7a2c4297fc","tid":969371,"uid":47123,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"4fc0691b7a46b20c31dca88cab9843337ae65d09","tid":969371,"uid":15950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d51bf8ca705fee7fa6780f5d8a0e65a35cbf323","tid":969371,"uid":47123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T04:22:05.000Z","msg":"雖然雪條款款都係回憶<br />\n但我唔念舊情<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個係美食家嘅專業！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T04:26:15.000Z","msg":"你係雪糕派嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T04:28:05.000Z","msg":"雪糕嘅口感唔係結咗冰嘅果汁可以比係上<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"189582582f4266f580c95b2e244cd3e5f0e552b6","tid":969371,"uid":215215,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T04:32:55.000Z","msg":"&nbsp;藍戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e04dafb7b80f1213bba3902d87533c2a0d4123f9","tid":969371,"uid":56111,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"189582582f4266f580c95b2e244cd3e5f0e552b6","tid":969371,"uid":215215,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T04:32:55.000Z","msg":"&nbsp;藍戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T04:35:20.000Z","msg":"藍鐵神<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1899389043f532c3397eb13ba49ad24ec1fefe21","tid":969371,"uid":47674,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T04:42:29.000Z","msg":"雪條冇脆皮搵鬼食<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"461831d7193f8963f7581bec9f5d2ea835fbdbcc","tid":969371,"uid":33359,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T04:45:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2065000/2065927/IMG_6601_600.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2065000%2F2065927%2FIMG_6601_600.JPG&h=fd5448eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌打"},{"pid":"82dbdfa3bb9f47a1fbf0671279e5f837c